On Wed, 18 Aug 1999 18:04:26 -0700 (PDT), you wrote:

>
>Someone really got taken then. On my server they go for 40pp to 75pp tops.
>most of the people I've talked to on others said it was around the same
>price.

Please tell me you're not serious that's how much they go for?? I met
a high level dwarf paladin in Rivervale the other day, had a nice chat
with him, joked around a little, and before he left he handed me a
pair of these gloves for free!!

And now I feel really bad that's how much they're worth! Ok, it's
peanuts to him, but to me that's still rather a lot of money!!
